<lb n="0968b11" ed="B"/>山不正貌</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>藞苴</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0968b1107" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">藞力瓦切苴側下切</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>篾</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0968b1116" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">莫結切析竹筠也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>襯</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0968b1124" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">初覲切</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>隳</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0968b1128" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">許規切毀
<lb n="0968b12" ed="B"/>也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><g ref="#CB05510"/></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0968b1203" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">正作鐙丁鄧切鞍<g ref="#CB05510"/>也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>薅</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0968b1213" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">呼高切<g ref="#CB15072"/>去田草也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><g ref="#CB21773"/></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0968b1222" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">音感覆也</note></p></cb:def></entry></cb:div>
